&gt; ### Release 0.8.2 (2018/08/21)
&gt;
&gt; * Part of bytecode that javac generates for `switch` statement on `java.lang.String` values with a small number cases is now correctly filtered out during generation of report (GitHub [#730](https://github.com/jacoco/jacoco/pull/730)).


so that for corrected example

```
class Example {
    public void myMethod(String let) {
        switch (let) {
        case &quot;A&quot;:
